item.title: Does UX = UI?
item.content: <p> <a href="http://www.uxisnotui.com/">A lot </a><a href="http://www.helloerik.com/ux-is-not-ui">of people</a> <a href="http://uxmovement.com/products/t-shirt-ux-is-not-ui/">are talking about</a> <a href="http://blog.careerfoundry.com/the-difference-between-ux-and-ui-design-a-laymans-guide/">this</a> <a href="http://www.slideshare.net/nicolasdemange/ux-is-not-ui-10294039">topic.</a>&nbsp;But is there much substance there?</p>
